title: GTA V - Non Stop Pop (Full 42 songs - 320kbps)
description:
This is extracted directly from GTA V original paid game. I did not find any other torrent for this so I wanted to upload.
There are a lot of torrents for GTA V's soundtrack, but non of them have full 42 songs for the Non Stop Pop station, usually only 16 songs, NO extra songs from PC/Next-gen console version.

I manually added track names, authors, year for every song individually, album art...

Kind of a lot of boring work, so I hope you appreciate my little work. :)
